<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>SING HIS PRAISES</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Lawp takin chawian chiet hitiu,
 Chamna Lalpa hungpieng chuh;
 A Lalchutphah, Ami thiengtho, A Lallukhuk hun nusien,
 Eihaw gilo a vaite hukdamna lam ei hun hilh hi,
 Pakchau uo, chitin pautin in Lalpen chuh chawian chiet un.

[V2]
 Pakchakna-haita puonna,
 Vannuoi tawp tieng geiin le;
 Nicheng, kum chengin pahchakna chuh
 Hai puona kumsawt in,
 Lei leh van beih nungin le
 Angel vamte tawh pakchai tiu.

[V3]
 2. Bawng In tawmah hung piengin,
 Gan kuongah hung kuol mah lele;
 Amah milien ahi, A gamin tawp tikni nei puona,
 Sak Thang, Sim leh Mala um thihna dailim nuoia chu ten;
 A Lalna pakchan nicheng, tha cheng, kum cheng pung zel un au.

[V4]
 3. Eden huona Setan in I Lallukhuk ei chuhthak khah,
 Tuhin chuh Lalpa Isu'n A zo a, ei hun pie kit tai;
 Zieziekchun nungak tangval, naupang, atek, a khang mitin,
 Lalpen te Lalpen pakchan tui kinawk guolin la sau in.

[V5]
 4. Leia mipi simsen loh leh van Angel simsen loh tawh,
 Aw Lalpa, Na hehpihna thukzie, letzie, sauzie, sanzie;
 Cha neihsun le hawilo a kei u di'n na hun sawl ziekin,
 Ka aw neih cheng u leh hattawp in tuhin ka hun pak chau.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>52</hymn_number>
</song>